Put 2L of water in the pot
Place the pot with water on the fire
Let water bolied (100 C)
add 20g of Salt into water when water boiled
After salt melted
Toss Pasta into Pot
mix Pasta in pot in 1 minutes by stirring
keep stirring in 2 minutes
Taste pasta
If it's chewy and firm, it is done Al dente
If not, keep cooking in 1 - 2 minutes
keep taste pasta every 1 minute to get Al Dente
when it is done turn off fire
lift the pot
let it colander.
